    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add your <strong>balsamic sun-dried tomato paste</strong> to the pan with your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml] </span><strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for 4-5 min further or until the sauce thickens slightly</p>",
