    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>drained orecchiette</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken cacciatora-style sauce with fresh orecchiette</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
